channel.description: When i click on bank to open it , it logs me out!!

item.title: Help ASAP! With bank
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“tank nation, post:5, topic:551818”][quote author=sk8rdude461 link=topic=670736.msg4484985#msg4484985 date=1433443045]
The t2 packet error you are seeing is because you set the bank size too high.
in config.java set the BANK_SIZE to 350 or lower.
[/quote]

Ah yeah!! that makes sense, shit i was trying to upgrade the bank space…[/quote]
I believe the packet error comes about because the bank does not have enough inventory slots in the code.
If you modify the bank code in the client and increase it’s space there, then maybe you won’t get the t2 error.
